data.description: Wonderfully updated home on a corner lot in Alpine Village. Move in ready with 2 primary bedrooms, each with their own 1.75 ensuites and walk in closets. Newer flooring throughout and an additional half bath for guests. The open chef's kitchen has newer granite countertops and an abundance of storage to include 2 pantries, ready for all your cooking and entertaining desires. Enjoy your fully fenced yard which includes an RV Gate, RV Hooks ups, shed for extra storage and 2 covered patios as well as great outdoor kitchen area. The two car garage has plenty of built in storage with an additional work area. Come see today!
